saddletweed
Homonym Number:
Word Class:adjective
Sense Number:
Definition:[of trousers] made of strong woollen twill fabric [teamed with tartan shirt and hobnailed boots as a high-country worker's 'uniform'].
Origin:[none]
Register:
Register 2:
